title: League People OCE Community (Facebook Group)
body:
League People OCE - Community specific to the OCE Community and what the run down is with Patches, Oceania Challenger Series, Servers, RP Price increases and more! Basically anything related to League of Legends and for the Oceanic Region! 

Meet and greet new players! Find people to play with and improve at the game! 

Come join the community! Have fun! Keep up to date :)
